OL,7,FNorth Wales Chief Fire Officer Dawn
OL,8,FDocx and Mid and West Wales Chief Fire
OL,9,FOfficer Roger Thomas KFSM said they
OL,10,Faccepted the reports' findings and
OL,11,Fwent on to apologise to staff.
